HMV Mulls Bids for Bookstore Chain, Waterstone’s, Sky Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-05-12T19:26:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/hmv-mulls-bids-for-bookstore-chain-waterstone-s-sky-reports.html
HMV Group Plc (HMV)  has received a number
of offers for its bookstore chain, Waterstone’s, following talks
with up to ten potential bidders, possibly including Change
Capital Partners LLP,  Sky News  reported, without attribution.
HMV’s adviser,  Nomura Holdings Inc. (8604) , set a deadline of today for
initial bids for Waterstone’s, Sky said, without saying where he
got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 